{"tid":2513926,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"古天奴重返英超，即將加盟愛華頓！","createTime":"2021-05-03T02:26:58.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-03T11:39:01.000Z","uid":31314,"like":19,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"0111283c4840d6acd03f72fa543e98eb50612a2a","tid":2513926,"uid":31314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T02:26:58.000Z","msg":"多間英國傳媒報道，巴西進攻中場菲臘比古天奴即將離開巴塞隆拿，重返英超，不過並非重投利物浦懷抱，而係<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">加盟紅軍死敵愛華頓麾下</span></span></strong>，據報<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong><span class=\"red\">轉會費只須3500萬鎊</span></strong></span>(約3.78億港元)，比2018年由利物浦轉投巴塞嘅1.45億鎊，身價大減1.1億鎊。<br />\n<br />\n古仔近期仍在養傷，今季提早收咧，佢同巴塞合約至2023年，不過轉會以來古仔喺巴塞表現都不如預期，反而上季外借到拜仁慕尼黑仲贏得包括歐聯冠軍嘅歐洲3冠王，巴塞一早想將佢出售，但搵唔到合適買家，在球會陷入財困之下，惟有賤賣古仔。<br />\n<br />\n之前曾有傳古仔重投利物浦，不過有唔少反對聲音，好多紅軍球迷都視古仔當日改投巴塞係背叛。愛華頓近年由安察洛堤領軍下，成績同表現都不斷上升，占士洛迪古斯今季在肥安旗下表現出色，佢打算簽入古仔，同J神合作踢雙中場，來季衝擊歐洲賽資格。<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.thenationalnews.com/image/policy:1.661572:1506348979/image/2017-09-25T091643Z_716562861_RC1480004AD0_RTRMADP_3_SOCCER-CHAMPIONS-SPM-LIV-PREVIEW.JPG?f=16x9&amp;w=1200&amp;$p$f$w=d1d507c\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thenationalnews.com%2Fimage%2Fpolicy%3A1.661572%3A1506348979%2Fimage%2F2017-09-25T091643Z_716562861_RC1480004AD0_RTRMADP_3_SOCCER-CHAMPIONS-SPM-LIV-PREVIEW.JPG%3Ff%3D16x9%26w%3D1200%26%24p%24f%24w%3Dd1d507c&h=07b3c08a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://www.hitc.com/static/uploads/hitcn/860/topshot_barcelonas_new_brazilian_midfielder_philippe_coutinho_sh_693368.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hitc.com%2Fstatic%2Fuploads%2Fhitcn%2F860%2Ftopshot_barcelonas_new_brazilian_midfielder_philippe_coutinho_sh_693368.jpg&h=845c7d0f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://tmssl.akamaized.net/images/foto/galerie/coutinho-fc-bayern-munchen-1566205098-24775.jpg?lm=1566205135\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftmssl.akamaized.net%2Fimages%2Ffoto%2